message.raw:
Runmanager api is now saving whatever type of strings it is given, rather
than encoding and saving as bytes. We will see if this causes any trouble.

Engage button now can't be clicked whilst parsing is in progress.

There are some more log lines

Fixed a bug with save data.

Set version to 2.0
